<div lang="en" dir="ltr" class="mw-content-ltr">
==Appearance of ranks inside VRChat ==
</div>

<div lang="en" dir="ltr" class="mw-content-ltr">
[[File:TrustRank_Example.png|right|frameless]]
</div>

<div lang="en" dir="ltr" class="mw-content-ltr">
The Safety and Trust system is designed to stay unobtrusive. A user's Trust Rank is visible only when the Quick Menu is open. This setting can be changed under "User Interface" > "Nameplate" or in the [[Special:MyLanguage/Action Menu|Action Menu]] under "Options" > "Nameplates."
</div>

<div lang="en" dir="ltr" class="mw-content-ltr">
*The text in the top left of the [[Special:MyLanguage/Nameplates|nameplate]] indicates the user's Trust Rank.
*The top right of the nameplate displays the user's avatar performance rank.
</div>

